Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.36,0:23:04.62,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3\3c&H744237&}いつまでもあなたを待ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.28,0:23:12.84,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3\3c&H44547B&}何回も　何度も伝えるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.84,0:23:18.42,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3\3c&H44547B&}どうなったって変えられぬ愛を
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.42,0:23:24.01,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3\3c&H44547B&}本当の美しいあなたを
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.01,0:23:29.55,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3\3c&H44547B&}ずっと前から僕は見てたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.55,0:23:32.31,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3\3c&H44547B&}大切なものひとつ　それは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.31,0:23:37.72,ED-JP,,0,36,0,,{\an3\fad(240,240)\blur3\3c&H44547B&}僕とあなたの幸せだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.86,0:22:27.43,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3\3c&H744237&}究竟隱藏在何處
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.07,0:22:32.63,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3\3c&H744237&}我無數次地尋找
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.06,0:22:38.53,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3\3c&H744237&}閃耀的銀河之中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.30,0:22:43.96,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3\3c&H744237&}那僅屬於我的美麗光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.83,0:22:47.75,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3\3c&H744237&}好了沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.75,0:22:50.57,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3\3c&H744237&}還差一點
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.57,0:22:53.36,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3\3c&H744237&}好了沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.36,0:23:04.62,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3\3c&H744237&}等你到天長地久
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.28,0:23:12.84,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3\3c&H44547B&}再一次  無數次傳達
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.84,0:23:18.42,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3\3c&H44547B&}無論如何不會改變的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.42,0:23:24.01,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3\3c&H44547B&}真正美麗的你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.01,0:23:29.55,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3\3c&H44547B&}我從前便一直關注
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.55,0:23:32.31,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3\3c&H44547B&}唯一珍貴的事物  那便是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.31,0:23:37.72,ED-CN,,0,40,0,,{\an9\fad(240,240)\blur3\3c&H44547B&}我與你的幸福吧
